data.description: Seller is offering $10,000 in use as you choose concessions to buy the interest down, for closing costs, or for minor repairs.  Welcome to the highly desired neighborhood of Rock Creek.  This 3 bedroom 2.5 bath home includes a beautiful kitchen with granite counter tops and stainless steel appliances, a separate dining area, a sunken living area with built in bookcases, and two bonus rooms.  Enjoy the Carolina nights on the covered front porch or the deck made for entertaining.  The is a golf course nestled in and throughout the subdivision as well.
